99
00:06:23,050 --> 00:06:25,659
This person beside me is a psychologist.

100
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:27,080
A lie detector.

101
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:30,520
Don't try lying in front of her.

102
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:35,370
(No lies, no betrayal.)
I killed her.

103
00:06:36,370 --> 00:06:37,129
Zhao Zimo.

104
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:37,539
Male.

105
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:38,369
Age, 25.

106
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:40,760
He was in a two-year relationship
with the deceased, Tang Tang.

107
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,779
They were married five months
when she was killed.

108
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:46,169
According to the note found at home,

109
00:06:46,170 --> 00:06:49,130
(No lies, no betrayal.)
Zhao Zimo threatened her with death.

110
00:06:49,690 --> 00:06:50,659
We found a taxi receipt

111
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:52,809
(Taxi Receipt)
from his home going

112
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:55,360
to the meat processing factory
on the 5th of November at night.

113
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,129
Also,

114
00:06:56,130 --> 00:06:59,289
after Piao Daguang accidentally
picked up Tang Tang's phone,

115
