Zhao Zimo tried to approach Piao Daguang
multiple times to retrieve her phone.

116
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:05,720
All of these clues point to one thing.

117
00:07:05,930 --> 00:07:08,929
And that is,
on the night Tang Tang was killed,

118
00:07:08,930 --> 00:07:11,129
Zhao Zimo tailed Tang Tang
to the meat processing factory.

119
00:07:11,130 --> 00:07:13,129
Then, he killed her and hid her body.

120
00:07:13,130 --> 00:07:16,160
So far, Zhao Zimo
is the biggest suspect in this case.

121
00:07:20,780 --> 00:07:21,930
I...

122
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:24,930
Yes.

123
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:26,720
Getting married

124
00:07:27,690 --> 00:07:28,840
