125
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:32,720
was not as happy as we imagined.

126
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:53,400
Where did you go?

127
00:07:54,340 --> 00:07:56,930
Why haven't you turned on the lights?
You scared me.

128
00:08:02,170 --> 00:08:04,400
