129
00:08:06,580 --> 00:08:08,480
I was working overtime.

130
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:12,210
No.

131
00:08:12,420 --> 00:08:13,840
No, Darling.

132
00:08:13,980 --> 00:08:15,339
What's wrong?

133
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,480
Go away!

134
00:08:23,290 --> 00:08:24,840
Darling.

135
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:27,570
Darling.

136
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:30,040
Darling.

137
00:08:32,410 --> 00:08:33,570
Darling.

138
