147
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:10,690
You have eyes only for your new lover.

148
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:12,080
Right?

149
00:09:14,010 --> 00:09:14,459
Zhao Zimo.

150
00:09:14,460 --> 00:09:16,810
What are you talking about?

151
