153
00:09:25,220 --> 00:09:27,330
Let me tell you what I did.

154
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:29,579
I went to make money.

155
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:30,409
Okay.

156
00:09:30,410 --> 00:09:32,330
You want to know what I did, right?

157
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:34,529
I go out early and
come back late every day

158
00:09:34,530 --> 00:09:37,129
