159
00:09:37,130 --> 00:09:37,819
Okay.

160
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:42,059
I need to pay for the rent, water, and
electricity, and I want to buy clothes!

161
00:09:42,060 --> 00:09:43,410
Enough!

162
00:09:44,730 --> 00:09:47,720
In the end, it's because I'm useless

163
00:09:47,730 --> 00:09:49,170
