172
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:22,210
Don't touch me!

173
00:10:25,610 --> 00:10:26,930
It happened so many times.

174
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:28,960
It wasn't like that before.

175
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:32,570
At that period of time, I was

176
00:10:34,370 --> 00:10:35,690
