177
00:10:38,250 --> 00:10:39,720
Then one day...

178
00:10:40,730 --> 00:10:42,880
Attack!

179
00:11:01,610 --> 00:11:02,760
Tang Tang.

180
00:11:14,940 --> 00:11:16,080
Zhao Zimo.

181
00:11:17,770 --> 00:11:19,050
Let's get a divorce.

182
00:11:21,410 --> 00:11:22,219
She...

183
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:23,930
